# 🎧 Cloudboi Records

A private artist archive website for music, videos, lyrics, and memories.

Built with:
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript
- Google Drive video embeds
- GitHub Pages hosting

────────────────────────────────────────────

#  FEATURES

 Password protected homepage
 Mobile responsive design
 Video section
 Audio player section
 Lyrics section loaded from TXT files
 Photo gallery
 Instagram link
 Smooth scrolling animations
 GitHub Pages compatible

────────────────────────────────────────────

#  PROJECT STRUCTURE

cloudboi-records/

index.html

music/
song1.mp3
song2.mp3
song3.mp3
song4.mp3

photos/
photo1.jpg
photo2.jpg
photo3.jpg
photo4.jpg
photo5.jpg
photo6.jpg

lyrics/
index.json
lyrics1.txt
lyrics2.txt

────────────────────────────────────────────

#  CHANGING THE PASSWORD

Inside index.html find:

if (p === 'lovefreddie')

Replace:

lovefreddie

with your own password.

Example:

if (p === 'cloudforever')

────────────────────────────────────────────

#  ADDING VIDEOS

Videos use Google Drive embeds.

STEP 1 — Upload Video To Google Drive

Upload your .mp4 video to Google Drive.

STEP 2 — Make Video Public

Right click the video → Share

Change access to:

Anyone with the link

STEP 3 — Copy Video Link

Example Google Drive link:

https://drive.google.com/file/d/1ABCXYZ123456/view

STEP 4 — Copy ONLY The File ID

From:

https://drive.google.com/file/d/1ABCXYZ123456/view

Copy:

1ABCXYZ123456

STEP 5 — Replace The iframe src

Find:

<iframe
  src="https://drive.google.com/file/d/PASTE_DRIVE_ID_1/preview"
  allow="autoplay"
  allowfullscreen>
</iframe>

Replace with:

<iframe
  src="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1ABCXYZ123456/preview"
  allow="autoplay"
  allowfullscreen>
</iframe>

────────────────────────────────────────────

#  ADDING MORE VIDEOS

Copy one full video card:

<div class="card fade-in">

  <div class="card-label">Video 5</div>

  <h3>New Video</h3>

  <div class="video-wrap">

    <iframe
      src="https://drive.google.com/file/d/FILE_ID/preview"
      allow="autoplay"
      allowfullscreen>
    </iframe>

  </div>

</div>

Paste it below the last video card.

────────────────────────────────────────────

#  ADDING AUDIO

Place .mp3 files inside:

music/

Example:

music/song5.mp3

Add Audio Card:

<div class="card fade-in">

  <div class="card-label">Track 5</div>

  <h3>New Song</h3>

  <audio controls>
    <source src="music/song5.mp3" type="audio/mpeg" />
  </audio>

</div>

Paste below existing tracks.

────────────────────────────────────────────

#  LYRICS SYSTEM

Lyrics are loaded automatically from TXT files.

STEP 1 — Create TXT File

Inside:

lyrics/

create:

lyrics3.txt

STEP 2 — Add Lyrics

Example:

Late nights in the studio
Clouds over the city

STEP 3 — Update index.json

Open:

lyrics/index.json

Example:

[
  {
    "title": "Already Yours",
    "file": "lyrics1.txt"
  },

  {
    "title": "Seasons",
    "file": "lyrics2.txt"
  }
]

Add another object:

{
  "title": "New Song",
  "file": "lyrics3.txt"
}

Final example:

[
  {
    "title": "Already Yours",
    "file": "lyrics1.txt"
  },

  {
    "title": "Seasons",
    "file": "lyrics2.txt"
  },

  {
    "title": "New Song",
    "file": "lyrics3.txt"
  }
]

────────────────────────────────────────────

#  ADDING PHOTOS

Place images inside:

photos/

Example:

photo7.jpg

Add Photo Block:

<div class="photo-item fade-in">
  <img
    src="photos/photo7.jpg"
    alt="Photo 7"
    loading="lazy"
  />
</div>

Paste below existing photos.

────────────────────────────────────────────

#  MOBILE SUPPORT

The website already supports:
- phones
- tablets
- desktop
- responsive layouts

────────────────────────────────────────────

#  CHANGING COLORS

Inside CSS:

:root {
  --green: #1db954;
}

You can replace colors.

Example:

--green: #ff4d8d;

────────────────────────────────────────────

#  UPDATING INSTAGRAM LINK

Find:

<a href="https://www.instagram.com/rjtttttttt?igsh=NDZobGhleW5qYWRq">

Replace with your own Instagram profile link.

────────────────────────────────────────────

#  HOSTING ON GITHUB PAGES
Your website URL becomes:

https://YOURUSERNAME.github.io/REPOSITORY-NAME/

────────────────────────────────────────────

#  IMPORTANT

File names are case-sensitive.

Example:

photo1.jpg

is NOT the same as:

Photo1.jpg

────────────────────────────────────────────

#  COMMON PROBLEMS

VIDEOS NOT LOADING

Check:
- Google Drive sharing is public
- iframe link uses /preview
- File ID is correct

AUDIO NOT PLAYING

Check:
- .mp3 exists in music/
- filename matches code exactly

LYRICS NOT SHOWING

Check:
- lyrics/index.json exists
- JSON syntax is valid
- TXT filenames match

IMAGES MISSING

Check:
- image exists in photos/
- filename matches exactly

